snippet.title: [RARE] Sonic Mania Collector's Edition Infomercial - 1996
snippet.description:
Take a look at recently unearthed footage from the SOA tackle box vault of a never before seen infomercial for Sonic Mania's Collector's Edition. You can really feel that '90s A E S T H E T I C. To order for your preferred console, check the links below.

Order here for PS4 ⇢ https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B01LVZ7YXP

Order here for PC ⇢ https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B01LVVBLPD

Order here for Xbox One ⇢ https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B01LW93WIT
